<!-- 입찰공고 실무흐름도 -->
<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-3">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-indigo-500">account_tree</span>
      입찰공고 실무흐름도
    </h2>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1">공고기간 확인 → 공고문 작성 → 나라장터 등록 → 개찰까지의 전체 절차</p>
  </div>

  <div class="p-6">
    <div class="mb-6 p-3 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-xl text-sm text-blue-800 flex items-start gap-2">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 mt-0.5" style="font-size:18px">info</span>
      <span><strong>공고기간 핵심</strong> 10억 미만 <strong>7일</strong> · 10~50억 <strong>15일</strong> · 50억 이상 <strong>40일</strong> · 긴급 <strong>5일</strong> (시행령 제16조)</span>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="mb-2">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px">flag</span>
          PHASE 1 — 공고 준비
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-blue-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">추정가격 확인 · 공고기간 결정</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• 추정가격 구간별 <strong class="text-blue-700">최소 공고기간</strong> 확인</li>
            <li>• 긴급공고(5일) 적용 가능 여부 판단 (천재지변 등 법정 사유만)</li>
            <li>• 기간 산정: <strong class="text-blue-700">공고일·입찰일 제외</strong>, 역일 기준</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span></div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-violet-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-violet-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-violet-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-violet-800 mb-2">공고문 작성</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• <strong class="text-violet-700">필수 기재:</strong> 입찰 건명, 입찰·개찰 일시, 참가자격, 입찰보증금, 낙찰 방법, 이행기간</li>
            <li>• <strong class="text-violet-700">첨부:</strong> 규격서·설계서 파일 준비</li>
            <li>• 특정 업체 유리 조건·특정 상표 기재 <strong class="text-red-600">금지</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span></div>

      <div class="mb-2">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px">flag</span>
          PHASE 2 — 공고 등록 · 진행
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-amber-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-amber-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-2">나라장터(G2B) 공고 등록</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• G2B 접속 → 입찰공고 등록 → 기본정보 입력</li>
            <li>• 규격서·설계서 첨부파일 업로드</li>
            <li>• 참가자격·낙찰방법 설정 → <strong class="text-amber-700">공고기간 설정</strong> → 승인·게시</li>
            <li class="text-xs text-slate-500">※ 추정가격 2천만원 초과: 나라장터 공고 필수</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span></div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-orange-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-orange-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-orange-800 mb-2">공고기간 중 관리</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• 입찰참가자 질의 응답 (모든 참가자에게 <strong class="text-orange-700">동일 답변</strong>)</li>
            <li>• 규격 변경 필요 시 → <strong class="text-orange-700">변경공고</strong> 필수 (공고기간 재산정)</li>
            <li>• 공고 취소 시 → 취소 사유 및 향후 계획 공지</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span></div>

      <div class="mb-2">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px">flag</span>
          PHASE 3 — 입찰 마감 · 유찰 시
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-green-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">입찰 마감 · 개찰</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• 입찰자 <strong class="text-green-700">2인 이상</strong> 참가 시 입찰 성립</li>
            <li>• 전자입찰 시스템 자동 개찰 → 낙찰자 결정</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span></div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-teal-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">6</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-teal-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-teal-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-teal-800 mb-2">유찰 시 재공고입찰</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• 재공고 기간: 최초 공고기간의 <strong class="text-teal-700">절반 이상</strong> (최소 5일)</li>
            <li>• 입찰조건은 최초 공고와 <strong class="text-teal-700">동일</strong></li>
            <li>• 재공고에도 유찰 → <strong class="text-teal-700">수의계약</strong> 전환 가능</li>
            <li class="text-xs text-purple-600">※ 한시적 특례(~2026.6.30): 1인 입찰 시 재공고 없이 바로 수의계약 가능</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <details open class="mt-8 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
      <summary class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-500">info</span>
        <span class="font-semibold text-slate-700">참고 안내</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 ml-auto">공고기간 비교 · 감사대비</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="p-4 space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500">compare</span>
            <div class="w-full">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">공고기간 비교표</h4>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
                <div class="p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 text-center">
                  <div class="font-bold text-blue-800">10억 미만</div>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mt-1">7일+</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">재공고 5일+</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-3 bg-violet-50 rounded-lg border border-violet-100 text-center">
                  <div class="font-bold text-violet-800">10~50억</div>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-violet-600 mt-1">15일+</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">재공고 8일+</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-3 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg border border-amber-100 text-center">
                  <div class="font-bold text-amber-800">50억 이상</div>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600 mt-1">40일+</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">재공고 20일+</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-3 bg-red-50 rounded-lg border border-red-100 text-center">
                  <div class="font-bold text-red-800">긴급</div>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600 mt-1">5일</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">법정 사유 필수</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-500">gavel</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">감사 대비 체크리스트</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-lg mt-0.5">warning</span><span><strong>공고기간 부족</strong> — 추정가격 구간별 최소기간 착각 (7일 vs 15일)</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-lg mt-0.5">warning</span><span><strong>긴급공고 남용</strong> — 예산 소진 목적은 긴급사유 아님</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-lg mt-0.5">warning</span><span><strong>변경공고 누락</strong> — 규격 변경 후 변경공고 없이 진행 시 무효</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-lg mt-0.5">warning</span><span><strong>참가자격 과다 제한</strong> — 특정업체 유리 조건 설정 시 경쟁 제한</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</div>
